and the name are being passed into

19
00:01:08.595 --> 00:01:11.946
the color palette dynamically,
which makes it reusable.

20
00:01:11.946 --> 00:01:18.430
And I've also linked to the right
place in the documentation.

21
00:01:18.430 --> 00:01:22.371
The second part is making sure that the
page title will be the name of the color

22
00:01:22.371 --> 00:01:24.478
palette instead of the name of the page.

23
00:01:24.478 --> 00:01:28.480
So that's what we just discussed as well.

24
